name: Emily Sevilla
text: Guys here are super nice and accommodating. Pizza and bread sticks are my favorite. Thanks again.

name: Kevin Brooks
text: Okay pizza but their sandwiches are terrible. The Philly cheese steak was the WORST I have ever had!

name: ASAP Pest Control
text: These guys are really friendly and food is always hot. Will definitely be buying from this place again.

name: Tim Stine
text: Wings came out cold after pizza and bread sticks. Ordered honey BBQ wings. They bake Buffalo wings and then put honey BBQ on top of it.

name: Mary Selvadoss
text: Easy to order and always ready in time and they always have good deals . Spicy wings are great for a weekend get together.

name: Chris Burdette
text: Consistent good pan pizza. I always ask for a little extra sauce.

name: Joseph Ng
text: Horrible. Over an hour and a half wait for cold pizza. When we called the store to ask what was going on the shift manager was thoroughly unhelpful, rude, and disrespectful. He had the audacity to mock the fact that I have also worked â€¦More

name: Robert Bastian
text: The worst pizza we have ever eaten (carry-out). The crust was bigger than the toppings and the sausage tasted freezer burned. Please avoid. Picture of pizza provided.

name: Jay henning
text: The slowest!! 2 mediums took over an hour and we did carry out!

name: Paul Dollar
text: Worst place to order pizza in Damascus. Never enough employees to fulfill and deliver orders. Always way behind in their time.

name: Dave D
text: Carry out and delivery only, no eat-in.   The pizza has always been as expected.

name: Chereen dorsey
text: Greasy, barely any toppings, not worth the money!!

name: Karen Illescas
text: Had to wait 3 hours to get my order and when call asking for my food firt they put me on hold 3 times and then this girl tells me is because short stuff never order from here again...

name: zhihao lin
text: thank you for the frozen pizza and 3hr delive
